@startuml seq-prd-multiuser-queue
title TN-02 — Hàng Đợi Khi Nhiều Du Khách Cùng Vào 1 POI
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

actor "DEV-001" as D1
actor "DEV-002" as D2
actor "DEV-003" as D3

participant "QueueManager"   as Q
participant "RateLimiter\n(Semaphore max=10)" as S
participant "Audio/TTS"      as Audio

D1 -> Q : Enqueue(DEV-001, POI-A, Enter)
D2 -> Q : Enqueue(DEV-002, POI-A, Enter)
D3 -> Q : Enqueue(DEV-003, POI-A, Enter)

Q -> Q : Dedup 2s\nsort Tap>Enter>Near

Q -> S  : Acquire(DEV-001) → slot 1/10 → delay 0ms
S -> Audio : [t=0ms]   Play DEV-001

Q -> S  : Acquire(DEV-002) → slot 2/10 → delay 80ms
S -> Audio : [t=80ms]  Play DEV-002

Q -> S  : Acquire(DEV-003) → slot 3/10 → delay 160ms
S -> Audio : [t=160ms] Play DEV-003

Audio --> S : Done × 3 → Release slots

note over D1, Audio
  ✅ 3 thiết bị đều nghe — spread 80ms/slot — max 10 đồng thời
end note

== Dedup: cùng thiết bị trigger 2 lần trong 2s ==
D1 -> Q : Enqueue(DEV-001, POI-A) lần 2
Q -> Q  : IsDuplicate = true → **SKIPPED**
@enduml
